<p>That is one of the rare posts that need a comment from me before making it public, and I have not found the time to do that yet because almost all of my time is hijacked by the constant need to find ways to bring in enough money to keep our work alive.</p><p>I apologize for not having explained this immediately, and I will make a point of notifying those whose posts have not been approved for the same reason.</p>
